    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior retains a strong shine, though a close inspection will reveal some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the leather seats show some light creasing but no tears, and all electronic features are fully functional. Mechanically, it runs smoothly with a documented service history, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
      "price": 34500.0,
