    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector\u2019s dream, preserved in showroom condition since the day it was driven off the lot. The exterior boasts a flawless, deep-gloss finish with absolutely no swirls, chips, or imperfections, protected by a high-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains that genuine new-car scent; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and tight, completely free of creases or bolster wear. Every technological feature and convenience option functions perfectly, and the mechanical performance is indistinguishable from new, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history performed exclusively by authorized technicians. It has been garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did on delivery day.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
